title: Hint 1: Memory Weights
text: Consider what processes in digitization take up the most storage space on the computer.

title: Hint 2: Large Data Sets
text: When dealing with large files and extensive data, what computing technology would help manage and store this better?

title: Hint 3: Distributed Computing
text: \"Distributed computing\" can mean a system where computing tasks such as storing data are spread out across multiple computers to help manage large tasks. Use this to manage limited storage capacity.
